Package: SWATrunR
Type: Package
Title: Running SWAT+ and SWAT2012 Projects in R
Version: 1.1.0.9017
Authors@R: person("Christoph", "Schuerz",
                email = "c.schuerz@posteo.org",
                role = c("aut", "cre"),
                comment = c(ORCID = '0000-0002-7204-5828'))
Maintainer: Christoph Schuerz <c.schuerz@posteo.org>
Description: SWATrunR links your SWAT+ and SWAT2012 projects on a hard
        drive with your modeling work flows in R. You can specify simulation
        outputs, modify model paramaters, and control many SWAT simulation
        parameters from R. SWATrunR returns simulations in a tidy format,
        offers parallel computing, and incremental saving of simulations in data
        bases.
